data.description: Situated in one of the most sought-after locations, this property offers the best value in West Wash Park.  This 2 bed, 1 bath home is being sold as-is, inviting you to bring your ideas, creativity and vision to update with a possible remodel, scrape, addition or pop top.  This Southern facing, corner lot holds endless possibilities.  Original charm found throughout the home includes gleaming hardwood floors, brick and glass front door detailing, and a lot of natural light.  Spacious yard offers an oversized back deck and detached one-car garge.  Enjoy the convenience of being 3 blocks from Wash Park, Light Rail, Whole Foods, and neighborhood favorite coffee shops and restaurants.  This central location further offers easy access to I-25, University of Denver, Cherry Creek North, Downtown, and Pearl and Gaylord Street shops and restaurants.  Don't miss this prime opportunity to customize your dream home in Wash Park!
